	bool "RS-485 on USART3"
	default n
	depends on STM32H5_USART3
	---help---
		Enable RS-485 interface on USART3. Your board config will have to
		provide GPIO_USART3_RS485_DIR pin definition. Currently it cannot be
		used with USART3_RXDMA.

